    "content": "\t\t\tThis ain't a love song   (bass)\r\n            \t\t(J.Bon Jovi/R.Sambora/D.Child)\r\n\r\nTranscribed by Dan\r\n\r\nThis song was a pain to transcribe.\r\nAny problems, let me know at dancorns@genie.co.uk\r\n\r\nListen to the CD for the timing.\r\n\r\n1st verse:\r\nStart from \"Baby ain't it funny........\"\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------|-----------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------|-----------|\r\nA|--7--6--5--5-4-2-0-----0--7/9-7-7-6-4-2-|2--2-4-2-0-|\r\nE|7-------------------0-------------------|-----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge:\r\nG|--------------------|-------------------|--------------------|\r\nD|--------------2-----|--------------2----|--------------2-----|\r\nA|0--0-2-3-4--4---4-2-|0-2--0-2--0-2---4--|0--0-2-3-4--4---4-2-|\r\nE|--------------------|-------------------|--------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\"I've cried and I've cried...........\"\r\n\r\nChorus:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------1-2----------------------|\r\nA|--6/7----4-4----0-0------------4-2--0|\r\nE|0-----7-------------4-2-0--0-4-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse II\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7--6--5--5-4-2-0-----0--7/9-7-7-6-4-2-|\r\nE|-------------------0-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------|-----------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------|-----------|\r\nA|--7--6--5--5-4-2-0-----0--7/9-7-7-6-4-2-|2--2-4-2-0-|\r\nE|7-------------------0-------------------|-----------|\r\n]\r\nBridge II[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------|-------------------|--------------------|\r\nD|------------------|--------------2----|--------------2-----|\r\nA|0--0-2-3-4----4-2-|0-2--0-2--0-2---4--|0--0-2-3-4--4---4-2-|\r\nE|------------4-----|-------------------|--------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus:\r\nG|--------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------1-2----------------------|\r\nA|7--7-6-4-2------4-4----0-0------------4-2--0|\r\nE|---------------------------4-2-0--0-4-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|7--7-6-4---4--2--0--0------------4-2--0--|\r\nE|---------7------------4-2-0--0-4---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nSolo:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|5---0---2--2-4-5---1/2-0-5-5-4-2-0------------------------|\r\nE|-----------------3-----------------3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3|[/tab]\r\n\r\nBridge III\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------|-------------------|--------------------|\r\nD|------------------|--------------2----|--------------2-----|\r\nA|0--0-2-3-4----4-2-|0-2--0-2--0-2---4--|0--0-2-3-4--4---4-2-|\r\nE|------------4-----|-------------------|--------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nChorus II\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|7--7-6-4---4--2--0--0------------4-2--0--|\r\nE|---------7------------4-2-0--0-4---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------|\r\nD|-------2-4-2----|\r\nA|0--0-4-------4--|\r\nE|---------------0|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|7--7-6-4---4--2--0--0------------4-2--0--|\r\nE|---------7------------4-2-0--0-4---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|7--7-6-4---4--2--0--0------------4-2--0--|\r\nE|---------7------------4-2-0--0-4---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nEnd:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--|\r\nD|--|\r\nA|7-|\r\nE|--|[/tab]\r\n\r\nThere are a few minor variations in the final choruses\r\nbut I have not tabbed them out 'cos I am too idle!!!!!:-)\r\nHowever it is about 85% note perfect.",
